}\\\\n+{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"tool_use\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T04:04:52.750Z\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"tool_name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"grep_search\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"tool_id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"grep_search_1776398692750_0\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"parameters\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"pattern\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"class PerformedPart\\\\\\\"}}\\\\n+{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"tool_result\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T04:04:53.635Z\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"tool_id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"grep_search_1776398692750_0\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"success\\\\\\\"}\\\\n+{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"message\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T04:04:57.693Z\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"role\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"assistant\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"I'll check `my-claw/tools/senseweave/render/rules/` to understand the implementation patterns of\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"delta\\\\\\\":true}\\\\n+{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"message\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T04:04:57.708Z\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"role\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"assistant\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\" other render rules and see if `CallResponseRule` follows the established architecture.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"delta\\\\\\\":true}\\\\n+{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"tool_use\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T04:04:57.754Z\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"tool_name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"list_directory\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"tool_id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"list_directory_1776398697754_0\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"parameters\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"dir_path\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"my-claw/tools/senseweave/render/rules\\\\\\\"}}\\\\n+{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"tool_result\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T04:04:57.897Z\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"tool_id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"list_directory_1776398697754_0\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"success\\\\\\\"}\\\\n+{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"message\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T04:04:59.711Z\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"role\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"assistant\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\