sdp/verification/t-015-verify.md:13:The implementation of the MIDI vocabulary store in `src/cypherclaw/midi_vocabulary_store.py` matches the requirements. The schema migration is idempotent and includes all requested fields: `id`, `source_file`, `kind`, `interval_pattern_json`, `duration_pattern_json`, `source_key`, `source_tempo`, and `harmonic_context_json`. The `ingest_extracted_fragments` helper correctly maps the payload from `extract_midi_fragments` (implemented in T-014) to the database rows.
