roject's documentation style and terminology. The mathematical definitions align perfectly with the code in `src/sdp/learning/fitness_db.py` and `src/sdp/learning/thompson.py`.\n\n## Security\nNo security vulnerabilities, secrets, or unsafe practices were introduced.\n\n## Quality\nThe documentation is high-quality, precise, and technically accurate. \n- **Tests**: `pytest tests/test_learning_fitness_db.py tests/learning/test_thompson.py tests/learning/test_backfill.py` passed (46 passed).\n- **Linting**: `ruff` and `mypy` are clean on the relevant source files.\n- **Markdown**: `markdownlint` is clean on the updated document.\n\n## Issues Found\n- [ ] No issues found.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe documentation is thorough and accurately reflects the underlying math and implementation. No further changes are required. The stale hardening check regarding `_monitor_show_state` at line 345 of `src/sdp/cli.py` remains invalid as the file is only 35 lines long and correctly implements the re-export.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-019 @20260512t162342zc-verify.md"}}
